Definition: administering vaccine only to people in close contact with an isolated infected patient
Example: prevents the spread of a highly infectious disease by surrounding the patient with a ring of immunization
Synonyms: inoculating, administering, vaccine, only, to, people, in, close, contact, with, an, isolated, infected, patient, prevents, the, spread, of, a, highly, infectious, disease, by, surrounding, ring, immunization
Category: noun.act
